{"blocks":[{"key":"3gf3m","text":"On the clean bench, take 50 mg of scented glands and put them into a pre-cooled mortar to ensure that the liquid nitrogen has never passed the sample, quickly grind the sample into powder, add 1 ml TRIZOL, mix the tissue powder with TRIZOL, and put it into In a centrifuge tube, stand at room temperature for 15 min.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ea063","text":"    ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1},{"key":1,"offset":2,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"9ekob","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"temperature","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"error_temperature":false,"guid":"E09FBDC0A29711ED82B3E37A160A17CF","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"temperature":"","unit":32}},"1":{"type":"duration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":900,"guid":"25B67050A29A11ED82B3E37A160A17CF","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"start":null}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"90a4m","text":"Add 200 ml of chloroform, shake the centrifuge tube for 15 s to mix the chloroform and TRIZOL well.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5lgtu","text":"Stand at room temperature for 10 min, put it in a refrigerated centrifuge and centrifuge at 4°C, 12000r/min, 15 min.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"55e8c","text":"  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"blaep","text":"    ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":1,"offset":0,"length":1},{"key":2,"offset":2,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"ae8gd","text":"   ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":3,"offset":1,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"9k964","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"duration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":15,"guid":"0BDDEC30A29A11ED82B3E37A160A17CF","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"start":null}},"1":{"type":"temperature","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"error_temperature":false,"guid":"167BF880A29A11ED82B3E37A160A17CF","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"temperature":"","unit":32}},"2":{"type":"duration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":600,"guid":"1AD8C2F0A29A11ED82B3E37A160A17CF","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"start":null}},"3":{"type":"shaker","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":900,"error_shaker":false,"error_temperature":false,"guid":"5B215D90A29A11ED82B3E37A160A17CF","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"scientificNotation":{"shaker":false,"temperature":false},"shaker":"12000","start":null,"temperature":"4","temperatureUnit":10,"unit":33}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"jjlh","text":"After centrifugation, the solution was separated into three phases. Take the upper aqueous phase into a new centrifuge tube, add three times the volume of ethanol to mix, stand at room temperature for 10 min.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"aqi0a","text":"    ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1},{"key":1,"offset":2,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"8m5nu","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"temperature","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"error_temperature":false,"guid":"6ADAFB00A29B11ED82B3E37A160A17CF","id":0,"label":"","scientificNotation":false,"temperature":"","unit":32}},"1":{"type":"duration","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":600,"guid":"6D369E40A29B11ED82B3E37A160A17CF","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"start":null}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"34sm7","text":"Add the mixed solution to the purification column, centrifuge at 12000r/min at 4°C for 2 min, repeat three times to ensure that ethanol is removed.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3fndm","text":"  ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":0,"length":1}],"data":{}},{"key":"27d95","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"shaker","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"duration":120,"error_shaker":false,"error_temperature":false,"guid":"CACDF800A29B11ED82B3E37A160A17CF","id":0,"label":"","pause":null,"preset":[],"scientificNotation":{"shaker":false,"temperature":false},"shaker":"12000","start":null,"temperature":"4","temperatureUnit":10,"unit":33}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"d9mio","text":"Add RNase inhibitors to ensure that the RNA will not be degraded, and mark the outside of the centrifuge tube.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"396ip","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"fj0tm","text":"Check RNA purity and concentration, and confirm RNA integrity by electrophoresis.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
